data.description: This great family ranch style home in a quiet neighborhood with quick access to all the best of Roanoke is move in ready for you! Upgrades include a new roof, new HVAC system, and updated bathroom. Fenced in backyard offers plenty of entertainment space and room for pets to run free or children to play. Large unfinished basement makes potential for great entertainment space, man cave, kid zone, or large office. New lights and ceiling fans to be installed prior to closing. Come check out this adorable and affordable home before it's gone. Come see today!
